The damping factor Γsurf is related to the limitation of mean free path of electrons bounded inside an MNP. It can be calculated through the scattering mechanism of a free electron by the surface of MNP. We use the following formula for considering contribution of size limitation in the energy dissipation8013Γsurf=AvfLeff.\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
